node.text:
Today we’re taking it to the field. You can also do this on a treadmill

1. 50 meter sprint 
-25 push ups
2. 50 meter sprint 
-8 cycle jumps each leg
3. 50 meter sprint 
-15 V ups
4. 50 meter sprint 
-7 broad jumps 
5. 50 meter sprint 
-30 shoulder taps.
6. 50 meter sprint 
-10 burpees jumps 

Rest 3 mins and repeat 2 more times.
@fitnessculturetraining @gymshark 
🎥 @alexluscombe_photography 
Song Astronaut in the Ocean by Masked Wolf #trackworkout #hiitworkout #fatlosscardio #circuittraining

node.text:
Quick, easy, and can be done anywhere. 
100 air squats
100 push-ups
100 sit ups. 
It’s amazing how something so simple can leave you wiped out!

node.text:
Legs Legs Legs! Always enjoyed getting through a leg workout. Well balanceds legs don’t happen by chance. Proper training and consistency. Swipe and save! 

1. Shark squats (can sun in back squats. 
3x12 reps + 8 reps after a 15 second pause. 2 mins rest.

2a good morning 3 x 8
Superset
2b barbell step ups. 3 x 8.

3a leg press 3 x 12. 3 second eccentric.
Superset 
3b leg extension 3 x 15 reps

Training program - @fitnessculturetraining 
Shirt 
@gymshark

node.text:
Are you or someone you know suffering from Invisible Lat Syndrome? ILS effects more gym goes than you might realize. Training only the muscles they see in the mirror while forgetting the important back muscles. This is exactly why we created the “DRIVE” program. Now you can bench your heart out while also incorporating proper back exercises to make sure you stay healthy and don’t end up looking like a gym douche. 
Check out @fitnessculturetraining for all the details
